  "title": "MANAGER",
  "description": "<p>Job Responsibilities:</p><p>• Part of the tender team participates in tendering civil and infrastructure projects.</p><p>• Involving in preliminary stage, design & tender stage, construction stage to e</p><p>nsure delivery of the project.</p><p>• Preparation of technical specifications and submissions of civil engineering work.</p><p>• Involving in the feasibility study and construction planning, and ensuring delivery of services accordingly to client’s requirements.</p><p>• Facilitate tender submission including coordinating with tender team, internal and external stakeholders, consultants, authorities on project requirements.</p><p>• Overseeing the construction activities, planning, implementation, and monitoring work schedules in accordance to the master and detailed work programme.</p><p>• Coordinate all related construction matters with subcontractor/consultant/client.</p><p>• Liaise with consultants for technical issues and coordinate with subcontractors on the site activities.</p>",
